c: 5
v: 17
t: "Pamasile paakufuulu aŵala ŵaakutiji: “Chisimu Allah ni Masihi mwanache jwa Maryam.” Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Ana nduni jwampaka akakwete chilichose chakumpinga Allah angasache Jwalakwe kun'jonanga Masihi (Isa) mwanache jwa Maryamujo, kwisa soni mamagwe ni wosope ŵali pachilambo? Soni Allah ni Nsyene uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, akugumbaga chaakusaka, soni Allah pachindu chilichose aŵele Jwakombola.”"